snippet.title: NAIRI: Tower of Shirin Windows PC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
NAIRI: Tower of Shirin is a cute graphic adventure with adorable visuals, compelling characters and engaging puzzles! 

NAIRI: Tower of Shirin is set to release on November 29th, 2018, simultaneously launching on Nintendo Switch and Steam.

**Win 1 of 25 copies of NAIRI: Tower of Shirin here: https://gleam.io/LQla7/nairi-tower-of... - entries close on November 28th 2018**

For more info, check out:
